snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator is coming to VR!
snippet.description:
PowerWash Simulator VR is coming to Meta Quest 2 in 2023! 

Grab and hold the power washer in virtual reality, aim with total precision and natural hand movement.Experience the filthy town of Muckingham in fully realised 360° glory.

Wishlist PWSVR here: https://ocul.us/3MILTMR

Getting into those dirty hard-to-reach spots has never been more satisfying!  

More info on PWS here: http://powerwashsimulator.com/

For more pressure-washing goodness, subscribe to our channel!
Follow our Twitter for daily satisfying content: https://bit.ly/TwitterPWS
Join the conversation on our Discord: https://discord.gg/powerwashsimulator
Follow us on TikTok for quick spray socials: https://bit.ly/PWSTikTok

#PowerWashSimulator #VR #MetaQuest #gaming #satisfying
